OL,3,CHundreds of steelworkers protest over
OL,4,CTata plans to axe up to 3,000 jobs
OL,6,FHundreds of steelworkers have marched
OL,7,Fthrough Port Talbot and Newport in
OL,8,Fprotest of Tata Steel's
OL,9,Fdecarbonisation plans, which could see
OL,10,Falmost 3,000 jobs axed.
OL,12,FIt comes after the company announced
OL,13,Fplans to close two blast furnaces at
OL,14,Fthe Port Talbot site in a move towards
OL,15,Fa greener method of steelmaking.
OL,17,FThis method, although better for the
OL,18,Fclimate, is less labour intensive and
OL,19,Fwill therefore require less workers.
