OL,6,FUnite and Community unions held
OL,7,Fdemonstrations on Saturday after .
OL,9,FSpeaking at the rally in Port Talbot,
OL,10,FCommunity General Secretary Roy
OL,11,FRickhuss described Tata's plans as
OL,12,F"disastrous".
OL,14,F"Today showed that Port Talbot,
OL,15,FNewport and South Wales -
OL,16,Fsteelworkers, politicians, local
OL,17,Fbusinesses and community groups - are
OL,18,Funited in opposing Tata's bad deal for
OL,19,Fsteel.
