OL,3,CHundreds of steelworkers protest over
OL,4,CTata plans to axe up to 3,000 jobs
OL,6,F"Make no mistake about it, what the
OL,7,Fcompany are proposing is bad for jobs,
OL,8,Fbad for our economy, bad for our
OL,9,Fenvironment and bad for national
OL,10,Fsecurity.
OL,12,F"As the steelworkers' union, we'll do
OL,13,Feverything we can in our power to
OL,14,Fstand up against Tata and the UK
OL,15,FGovernment's plan, including the last
OL,16,Fresort of industrial action as we set
OL,17,Fout yesterday."
