OL,6,FThe union is calling on Tata to look
OL,7,Fagain at a multi-union plan, which it
OL,8,Fsaid is supported by industry experts,
OL,9,Fthe Labour Party and Senedd members.
OL,11,FLabour MP for Aberavon Stephen Kinnock
OL,12,Fand Welsh Government Economy Minister
OL,13,FVaughan Gething both addressed the
OL,14,Frally in Port Talbot.
