OL,3,CHundreds of steelworkers protest over
OL,4,CTata plans to axe up to 3,000 jobs
OL,6,FAlan Coombs, Chair of the Multi-Union
OL,7,FCommittee at Port Talbot steelworks,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Steelworkers at Port Talbot are
OL,9,Fproud of our industry, and we are
OL,10,Fproud of our community which has come
OL,11,Fout in such a strong show of support
OL,12,Ffor us today.
OL,14,F"These are uncertain times, and many
OL,15,Fof us are anxious about what lies
OL,16,Fahead for Port Talbot.
OL,18,F"One thing is certain though -
OL,19,Fsteelworkers will fight tooth and nail
OL,20,Ffor the future of our industry and our
OL,21,Flivelihoods."
