OL,6,FA Tata Steel spokesperson said: "While
OL,7,Four #1.25 billion commitment with the
OL,8,FUK Government will ensure a long-term
OL,9,Fviable future for low CO2 steelmaking
OL,10,Fin the UK, our current business is
OL,11,Funsustainable.
OL,13,F"Much of our existing iron and
OL,14,Fsteelmaking operation in Port Talbot
OL,15,Fis at the end of its life, is
OL,16,Funreliable and inefficient, and
OL,17,Fcontributing to losses of #1.7million
OL,18,Fa day in the last quarter alone.
