OL,6,F"Our restructuring proposals would
OL,7,Fmean that we are able to sustain the
OL,8,Fbusiness as we transition to new
OL,9,Felectric arc furnace technology.
OL,11,F"We believe we have a very exciting
OL,12,Ffuture ahead, providing the high
OL,13,Fquality, low-CO2 steels that our
OL,14,Fcustomers in the UK and overseas are
OL,15,Fso desperate for.
