OL,6,F"Furthermore, producing steel from
OL,7,Fscrap that already exists in
OL,8,Fsignificant quantities in the UK
OL,9,Frather than importing iron ore and
OL,10,Fcoal from across the world, will be
OL,11,Fthe foundation for more resilient UK
OL,12,Fmanufacturing supply chains.
OL,14,F"Following the announcement of the
OL,15,Fcompany's restructuring proposals on
OL,16,F19 January, we have started a formal
OL,17,Finformation sharing and consultation
OL,18,Fprocess with our trades union
OL,19,Fcolleagues, which will continue for at
OL,20,Fleast 45 days.
